            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "heading_html": "<p>部署步骤</p>",
          "body_html": "<p>采用开放基础设施是一个战略过程。 <br><br>请遵循以下关键步骤以确保平稳过渡：</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "process",
          "variant": "process",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "zoom_on_click": true,
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3,
            "media_width": "1"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "intro",
              "title": "介绍",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>了解有效采用和实施该框架的基本步骤。 遵循这些准则可确保平稳过渡和最佳结果。</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "step",
              "title": "评估",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>评估当前的<strong>工作负载</strong>、<strong>功率限制</strong>和<strong>散热挑战</strong>，了解起点并确定需要改进的领域。</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "step",
              "title": "确定方案",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>使用 <strong>OCP Marketplace</strong> 查找符合具体<strong>密度</strong>和<strong>运营要求</strong>的<strong>硬件解决方案</strong>。</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "step",
              "title": "建立合作",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>与<strong>OCP 解决方案提供商</strong>合作，制定符合您需求的完整<strong>集成计划</strong>。</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "step",
              "title": "部署",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>先开展<strong>小规模实施</strong>，例如部署<strong>单个机架</strong>或<strong>试点舱</strong>，再扩展到<strong>整个设施</strong>。</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "summary",
              "title": "总结",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>通过遵循这些步骤，您可以有效地采用该框架并自信且高效地实现您的目标。</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
